Introducing Kupocards!

Available for purchase until Mon., Jul. 2, at 07:59 UTC


Here's a new way to purchase gems: Kupocards!

Kupocards are special in that they give you gems every day for 30 days in addition to being one of the best values for gems!

These Kupocards are only available for a limited time, so don't miss out on this great deal!

Read on for more details!

About Kupocards

Two types of Kupocards are available in the Gem Shop, and each can only be purchased once during this period, but you can have both Kupocards active simultaneously:

  • Kupocard
    　　　　Initial Gems: 150
    　　　　Daily Gems: 50 (for 30 days)
    　　　　Total: 1,650

  • Kupocard Gold
    　　　　Initial Gems: 500
    　　　　Daily Gems: 150 (for 30 days)
    　　　　Total: 5,000

Upon purchase, you will receive the Initial Gems immediately, and the Daily Gems will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your Daily Bonus for the next 30 days.

* These logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 30 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
